### Which Should You Use?

| | Project References | `include` with `../` |
|---|---|---|
| IntelliSense | ✅ | ✅ |
| Separate compile settings per project | ✅ | ✅ |
| Build caching | ✅ | ❌ |
| Setup complexity | Medium | Low |

If your project is growing and you care about build performance, go with **Option 1**. If you just want a quick fix to get IntelliSense working, **Option 2** will get you there in 30 seconds.

